ion state (427 lines)\n- realtime-hub.js: SSE event pub/sub (35 lines)\n- chat-service.js: legacy chat via codebuddy adapter (80 lines, deprecated)\n- config-service.js: F-017 runtime config manager — hot-reload via process.env, safe key whitelist, sensitive masking (337 lines)\nTRAPS:\n- SessionBindingService uses deferred init — always call ensureReady() before sync methods in async contexts\n- SessionBindingService persistence is fire-and-forget — tests must call flush() to verify file writes\n- messageRouter does not expose heartbeat hooks — Telegram heartbeat progress disabled after F-018 migration\n- Runtime bindings created via POST /api/bind do NOT auto-subscribe realtimeHub for cross-channel push (F-018 gap)\n- config-service originalEnvValues captured at module init; if env vars set after import, use setConfig first (which lazy-captures original) before reset | FIX: ensure env vars are set before module import in tests, or setConfig will lazy-capture the pre-modification value\nUPDATED: 2026-03-22\n","numLines":40,"startLine":1,"totalLines":40}}}
