{"type":"system","subtype":"task_progress","task_id":"a446cbf8a2cb64b3d","tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01AxNdFx22AqEXAnNaTghU15","description":"Writing .prizm-docs/src/utils/output-segmenter.prizm","usage":{"total_tokens":101179,"tool_uses":71,"duration_ms":1291726},"last_tool_name":"Write","uuid":"b0864994-051c-41ce-bcc2-d1d456bcddb4","session_id":"ac44fc5c-0407-4bd5-95fd-57d4b24826fc"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"content":[{"id":"toolu_vrtx_01PNUxaiYUiMbcoPRvcNrFP8","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizm-docs/src/utils/output-segmenter.prizm","content":"MODULE: src/utils/output-segmenter\nFILES: output-segmenter.js\nRESPONSIBILITY: Smart text segmentation at logical boundaries (code blocks, paragraphs) for Telegram messages\nKEY_FILES:\n- output-segmenter.js: 1 exported function + 4 private helpers, ~130 lines. Pure string transformation.\nDEPENDENCIES:\n- uses: none (no external dependencies)\n- imported-by: src/bot/telegram.js (createEditableStreamPublisher render() function)\nTRAPS:\n- Code block detection counts ``` occurrences — odd count means inside a block. This counts inline triple-backticks too; strings with malformed fences will misdetect.\n- Splits at paragraph (\\n\\n) first, then newline (\\n), then space — never hard-cuts at arbitrary byte boundary unless forced (no logical boundary found).\n- Default maxChunkSize is 3800, NOT 4096 — Telegram limit is 4096 but 3800 gives safety margin for metadata overhead.\n- findCodeBlockEnd searches for closing ``` AFTER the opening fence — if closing fence is missing (incomplete stream), it returns maxChunkSize as fallback (hard cut).\n- Replaces splitMessage() in the render() function inside createEditableStreamPublisher — NOT in the cross-channel push path (subscribeCrossChannel still uses splitMessage).\nCHANGELOG:\n- 2026-03-22 | add: initial module for F-020 smart output segmentation\nUPDATED: 2026-03-22\n"},"name":"Write","type":"tool_use"}],"id":"req_vrtx_011CZJDnsCz4N1SaSgZU9MhS","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":3027,"output_tokens":18,"cache_read_input_tokens":97603},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01AxNdFx22AqEXAnNaTghU15","session_id":"ac44fc5c-0407-4bd5-95fd-57d4b24826fc","uuid":"bf14bea1-90db-4ea7-962c-6baeb01bd9fe"}
